headline: Veris Residential (VRE) Surpasses Q3 FFO Estimates
summary: Veris (VRE) delivered FFO and revenue surprises of +33.33% and -2.06%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
